                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                <date>March 1. 1854</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Friend,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">You will probably chide me for<lb/> not having sent you my little\n                funeral address spoken<lb/> at the <add>?</add> of the late <persName>Mr.\n                    Touro</persName>. The truth is I preferred<lb/> reading your own remarks, which\n                I am fully assured,<lb/> will be more gratifying to your readers. The Asmonean<lb/>\n                I perceive has published <persName>Clapp's</persName> sermon in full,<lb/> and a\n                most wretched production of a rhymester<lb/> which, to save the credit of Jewish\n                talent ought<lb/> to have been suppressed. What do you think<lb/> the author of it\n                has even the ineffable conceit<lb/> to send it to <persName>Mr Shepperd</persName>\n                and ask for his<lb/> patronage! And thus it has been a subject of<lb/> ridicule in\n                the Picaynue<add>?</add> of this city.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Regarding the transmission of the<lb/> remains of your late\n                venerable friend, <persName>Mr. G.<lb/> Kursheedt</persName> will no doubt have\n                advised you.<lb/> It will not take place before <date>July</date> next.\n                    <persName>Mr.<lb/> K.</persName> has the sole management of the whole\n                affair;<lb/> a rather delicate duty is thus devolving upon<lb/> him. The question\n                will not be, how much<lb/> shall be done, but how little of the num-</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3k64bd2b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
