                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>in such a light, and I am much mistaken, if<lb/> you do not apply the same sentiments\n                to your<lb/> own case.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">We are anxiously awaiting the Bible. I<lb/> heard, that it is\n                finished. Let us have it, therefore<lb/> at your earliest convenience. I hope the\n                    en-<lb/><sic>terprize</sic> may be a profitable one, as it richly<lb/> deserves\n                to be.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Hoping that this may reach you in<lb/> your good health and\n                spirits</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">James K. Gutheim</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3k64bd2b/canvas/p3"
